creator: Seikami
descriptionHtml:
Imagine what your life would be when you find yourself in a strange isle, what would you do?

From this moment on, you are going to explore territories and work hard to build a dreamy farm! Hold on! Building a farm costs a lot! Do you have the money to spend on it?

When you are overwhelmed by life, please take a walk through fields, get close to your animals and win the trust of your villagers. Come and relax in this satisfying game!
